column2: select school, floor(schoolyear/#) as fyear, avg(absent) as absent,avg(enrolled) as enrolled ,    avg(cast(absent as real))/avg(cast(enrolled as real)) as frAbsent  from schoolattendance group by school,floor(schoolyear/#) ) , r as ( select  ,      a.*   from a    join schoollocation sl     on sl.fiscal_year=a.fyear     and sl.ATS_SYSTEM_CODE=a.school     and sl.LOCATION_CATEGORY_DESCRIPTION like &&& )select * from r
